      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"With no form on offer a market check could prove a helpful guide. 3. AMIRSOYLU represents the Mert Korkmaz stable and profiles well on paper being a three-year-old colt by Serhantay from Duru. Likely player. 1. AKERBEY is a three-year-old colt by Taykut out of Sargin. Receives a nice gate which can help and is expected to show promise. Worth including. 5. CAKIR METE holds claims being a son of Gelibolu from Kumru Hatun running for the Mehmet Akkus yard. Might feature. 4. ATAERI is a three-year-old colt by Baba Mevlut from Suphan. The good draw is sure to assist. Rates an interesting newcomer.\",\"runners\":[3,1,5,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
